SCOLD-style wrapping of (lib)httpserver
See https://github.com/etr/libhttpserver

The wrapping and packaging herein is licensed GPLv3.
See the LICENSE file nearby.

You will need the usual compilation tools.
Also:
dnf install -y {libmicrohttpd,libhttpserver}{,-devel} libmicrohttpd-doc gnutls{,-c++,-devel}
